---
title: "US20 — Inactivity alerts"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>NotificationsScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>CheckInactivity (rule-based)
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>WorkoutSession
  A->>B: inactivity alerts enabled
  C->>E: scan recent sessions vs weekly commitment
  E-->>C: no ended session for N days
  C-->>B: schedule alert
  B-->>A: "You have not worked out since..."
  note over E: delivered via NotificationGateway (local notifications)
